  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oil in a deep frying pan to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. In a small bowl, mix together Mexican Spice Blend, cumin, and nutmeg.",
    "3. Dip each tortilla into the water, then coat in the spice mixture.",
    "4. Fry tortillas in batches until crispy and golden brown, about 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "5. Remove fried tortillas from oil and place on paper towels to drain excess oil.",
    "6. Sprinkle crispy taco seasoning over fried tortillas and serve immediately."
  ],
